WEBVTT

00:04:59.866 --> 00:05:02.670
Sio kusema kwamba serikali
zisituweke salama--

00:05:02.694 --> 00:05:03.845
inabidi wafanye hivyo--

00:05:03.869 --> 00:05:06.464
ila tunahitaji ungalizi wa uwazi kwa umma

00:05:06.488 --> 00:05:08.729
na uwajibikaji kwenye utawala wa sheria.

00:05:08.753 --> 00:05:09.905
Wakati huo huo,

00:05:09.929 --> 00:05:13.802
wenye siasa kali huwa wanaua
jamii ya raia katika baadhi ya nchi.

00:05:14.198 --> 00:05:16.732
Tangu mwaka 2013 nchini Bangladesh,

00:05:16.756 --> 00:05:21.272
zaidi ya mabloga kwa idadi kubwa
na wanaharakati wa jamii

00:05:21.296 --> 00:05:24.229
wamechinjwa kabisa na
wafuasi wa siasa kali

00:05:24.253 --> 00:05:26.597
huku serikali ikichukua hatua kidogo sana.

00:05:27.008 --> 00:05:29.955
Kutoka mji wa Raqqa Syria,

00:05:29.979 --> 00:05:34.555
watu kama Ruqia Hassan na Naji Jerf
wameuwawa